data.title: Christel Khalil
data.meta_description: Christel Adnana Mina Khalil is an American actress. She is best known for her roles as Cornelia Hale in W.I.T.C.H. and Lily Winters in The Young and the Restless, the latter role earned her a Daytime Emmy Award in 2012.
